        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Apply the Science Act 2.0</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to seek to contract with the National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine to study COVID-19 immunity, including the durability of immunity resulting from an infection, a vaccine, or both.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
